               kpred:description  "Define the published site's theme in the graph: custom theme colors and, at minimum, a way to bind styles/components to page nodes. Custom theme colors and custom components may already be reachable via shadcn — the missing piece is expressing the style as triples so it round-trips like content. Minimum viable: theme color tokens as graph data; stretch: component-level styling." .

kb:gp-cloud-storage rdf:type ktype:Feature ;
